I"w<p>This is one of our research/passion projects. If a stock price series is
mean-reverting, we can trade on it and make a profit if we can accurately
estimate its mean and the standard deviation for the future. Kalman filter is
an excellent technique for doing that. To learn how, read our paper <a href="/assets/stock-price-forecasting-with-kalman-filter.pdf">here</a>.</p>
